      "span_text": "All cDNA clones from the J558-Neo tumors had the wild-type P1A sequence (Figure 2a ), while those recovered from the CTL-resistant tumor cell lines harbored mutations within the P1A epitope, the nine-AA peptide corresponding to positions 35-43 of the predicted P1A protein [CITATION_1] ."
